  "keyFeatures": [
    "Employee Lifecycle Management (onboarding, transfers, promotions, separation)",
    "Leave & Attendance with shift management and geolocation check-in",
    "Payroll processing with salary structures, income tax slabs, and gratuity",
    "Performance Management with goals, KRAs, and appraisal cycles",
    "Recruitment pipeline from job openings to offers",
    "Expense Claims and Employee Advances with approval workflows",
    "Mobile App (PWA) for leaves, attendance, and salary slips",
    "Regional overrides for India-specific tax calculations",
    "Integrated reporting and analytics across all HR modules"
